name: ToolbarItemOverflowBehavior
description: Defines the priority of the toolbar item to go inside overflow popover.

values.name: Default
values.description: The item is presented inside the toolbar and goes in the popover, when there is not enough space.
values._jsDoc:
/**
 * The item is presented inside the toolbar and goes in the popover, when there is not enough space.
 *
 * @public
 */

values.name: NeverOverflow
values.description: When set, the item will never go to the overflow popover.
values._jsDoc:
/**
 * When set, the item will never go to the overflow popover.
 *
 * @public
 */

values.name: AlwaysOverflow
values.description: When set, the item will be always part of the overflow part of ui5-toolbar.
values._jsDoc:
/**
 * When set, the item will be always part of the overflow part of ui5-toolbar.
 *
 * @public
 */
